Biryani Masala Powder, green cardamom pods, cinnamon, cloves, sliced tomatoes, green chillies, sliced onions, pudina (mint), coriander leaves, chicken pieces, Jeeraga Samba rice, and oil.
Step 1
Heat a vessel, add 200 ml of oil, add whole spices, 2 tbsp of ginger-garlic paste,

